<p>Paris prosecutors said a Chinese woman was arrested earlier this month in Barcelona and charged in connection with the September 16 theft of gold from France’s National Museum of Natural History [france24.com#1][bbc.com#1][scmp.com#1]. Investigators recovered around a kilogram of melted-down gold at the time of her arrest, and authorities estimate the stolen nuggets were worth roughly €1.5 million [bbc.com#1][france24.com#1]. The case centers on a break-in at the museum in Paris, where gold nuggets were taken from a display [scmp.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/K4zVkgBgIRmyFKDmafPbboKagYkUD35hzGor5AJRa9UxcvA4JDchZrkdVZCpKCh27odfPLQHQ5ts3zxSttDlLoJf_8ML9JTylidakBiBMu4tLbmrpfO7d5lrm6YVuGo7NCOr2tM194WKKI22tY2m6CzzMr82bz1nLi5OfgX2m-13K9BE0dcomr-_KdoGumal8hkI' alt='A burglar cut through doors with an angle grinder to steal gold from the mineralogy display at France’s National Museum of Natural History.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Scale of haul: Nearly six kilograms of native gold were taken, including a single 5kg nugget, with damages estimated at about US$2.26 million [straitstimes.com#1].</li><li>Suspect details: The charged suspect is a 24-year-old Chinese national, according to the Paris prosecutor’s office and reporting from the scene [scmp.com#1][france24.com#1].</li><li>Context in France: The theft came about a month before an audacious jewelry heist at the Louvre on a Sunday, underscoring pressure on French cultural institutions [scmp.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</li><li>Rising trend: Art theft specialists caution that museum heists have been increasing in recent years, adding urgency to security reviews [france24.com#1].</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Paris prosecutors: They reported the suspect’s arrest in Barcelona with about one kilogram of melted-down gold and confirmed charges were filed. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c62ez36ndp3o'>BBC News</a>)</li><li>Museum leadership: A former director described the burglars as an “extremely professional team,” highlighting the operation’s sophistication. (<a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/europe/article/3329828/chinese-woman-held-over-us1-million-gold-theft-paris-natural-history-museum'>South China Morning Post</a>)</li><li>Art theft specialists: Experts warned that museum heists have been on the rise in recent years. (<a href='https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20251021-chinese-woman-charged-over-gold-theft-at-paris-natural-history-museum'>France 24</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/europe/article/3329828/chinese-woman-held-over-us1-million-gold-theft-paris-natural-history-museum'>Chinese woman charged in Paris gold theft from Natural History Museum</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/chinese-woman-charged-over-gold-theft-at-paris-natural-history-museum'>Woman charged over theft of gold, including 5kg nugget, at Paris Natural History Museum</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20251021-chinese-woman-charged-over-gold-theft-at-paris-natural-history-museum'>Chinese woman charged over September gold theft at Paris Natural History Museum</a> - france24.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/21/world/europe/france-museum-theft-gold-nugget-arrest.html'>Suspect Charged in Paris Museum Heist (No, Not That One)</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/france/article/2025/10/21/paris-museum-thefts-chinese-woman-charged-with-stealing-over-1-million-in-gold_6746640_7.html'>Chinese woman arrested over gold theft from Paris Natural History Museum</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c62ez36ndp3o'>Woman charged after 1.5m euros of gold stolen from Paris museum</a> - bbc.com</li></ul>